          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "对，L1 的 SDR 存在飞书知识库文档里，每个决策写一篇结构化文档。PageIndex 树本身是索引，不是存储——Harness 的理念：记忆是索引，不是存储。真正的数据在知识库、Bitable、IM 消息里，PageIndex 只是他们的导航地图。",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:15",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f8871d4ca4b393be992f20f32",
        "msg_type": "text",
        "sender": {
          "id": "cli_a960fa124ea2dcef",
          "id_type": "app_id",
          "sender_type": "app",
          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "嗯，层级隔离确实是个优势。那存储方面呢？如果不用向量 DB，L1 层的 SDR 存在哪里？直接用飞书知识库的文档？",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:15",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f887acecacb39446ec438ef01",
        "msg_type": "text",
        "sender": {
          "id": "cli_a960fa124ea2dcef",
          "id_type": "app_id",
          "sender_type": "app",
          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "@向量数据库方案有一个根本问题：决策记录的关联是树状的、有层级的，向量检索是平面语义相似度。你在讨论支付模块的方案变更，向量 DB 可能召回完全不相关的另一个项目的方案。PageIndex 天然隔离了项目→阶段→议题的层级上下文。",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:15",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f88878e4a8b242f33cebdbce4",
        "msg_type": "text",
        "sender": {
          "id": "cli_a960fa124ea2dcef",
          "id_type": "app_id",
          "sender_type": "app",
          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "@关于上下文窗口的问题，PageIndex 不是把整棵树塞进去。PageIndex 树是一个索引结构，LLM 只在每层导航时读取当前层节点的 summary 来做决策——这是 O(log n) 的访问模式，不是全量加载。实际每个节点就几十个字摘要，不会爆窗口。",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:15",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f888578cacb224a51076815da",
        "msg_type": "text",
        "sender": {
          "id": "cli_a960fa124ea2dcef",
          "id_type": "app_id",
          "sender_type": "app",
          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "我还是支持向量数据库方案，更成熟稳定。PageIndex 依赖 LLM 推理导航，万一模型推理错了，整个检索路径就偏了。向量数据库的召回率至少是稳定的。",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:14",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f888c8e0b0b26ca22bcec4a36",
        "msg_type": "text",
        "sender": {
          "id": "cli_a960fa124ea2dcef",
          "id_type": "app_id",
          "sender_type": "app",
          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "PageIndex 这个方案我也认可，不过有个顾虑：如果项目变大，PageIndex 树节点太多，LLM 上下文窗口装不下怎么办？是不是需要分层裁剪？",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:14",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f88a3024a0b352ccf6cd0e121",
        "msg_type": "text",
        "sender": {
          "id": "cli_a960fa124ea2dcef",
          "id_type": "app_id",
          "sender_type": "app",
          "tenant_key": "1abd20e084069b82"
        },
        "updated": false
      },
      {
        "content": "关于记忆引擎的检索方案，我倾向于用 PageIndex 树替代向量数据库。主要原因是：1. 保留原生层级结构 2. LLM 推理导航更灵活 3. 更新成本低。大家觉得怎么样？",
        "create_time": "2026-04-25 22:14",
        "deleted": false,
        "message_id": "om_x100b51f88ae8c084b399bf9fee6acee",
        "msg_type": "text",
